---
layout: base
title: Home
---

<section class="linking padding about max-width" id="about">
    <h2 class="h2-title">
        About me
    </h2>

    <div class="about__container">
        <div class="about__container__text">
            <p class="salutation"><span class="ab">Hi</span> there,</p>
            
            <p class="name">I'm <span class="ab">Jan Deschacht!</span></p>
            
            <p class="synopsis">A <span class="ab">front end developer</span> from Ostend with a sense of design and responsiveness. For the moment I'm studying programming at Arteveldehogeschool.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about__container__img">
            <img src="{{ '/assets/images/about.png' | url }}" alt="Image of a cartoon" loading="lazy">
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="linking padding skills max-width" id="skills">
    <h2 class="h2-title">
        Skills
    </h2>

    <div class="skills__container">
